room_title: Escape room "Zombie Carnival" by Puzzle over This in Ocean City
room_address: 10445 Old Ocean City Blvd Unit 1, Berlin, MD 21811
room_description: You and your friends decide to go to the Zombie Carnival and have some fun. It'll be great! You're really excited until you enter through the door and it gets locked behind you! You try not to panic, but you know the carnival closes in an hour. You and your friends have to find a way out before the park closes and you're stuck here all night!
